metadata.name: Henry Scott Founder Pass #1/987
metadata.description:
Henry Scott Founder Pass is the early access token to discover the expedition of the cheeky, cute and funny french bulldog Henry Scott through WEB3 & NFT, Social Media, Online Education and the Crypto-Sphere. 
With a limited supply of 987 Founder Pass NFTs you will have an exclusive access to the fascinating adventures of French Bulldog Henry Scott.
